# 01 : BOOTSTRAP (v2)
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

§ STAGES
  stage0  : CSSLv3-compiler-in-Rust • throwaway • Cranelift-expedient
  stage1  : CSSLv3-self-hosted • own-x86-64-backend (§§ 14_BACKEND)
  stage2  : LoA-engine rewritten in CSSLv3 • Odin-LoA-v10 deprecated
  stage3  : ∀ version emits C99-tarball • reproducibility-anchor (R16)

§ STAGE-0 SCOPE
  host-lang : Rust stable (MSRV 1.75+) — throwaway artifact
  crates :
    cranelift-codegen  cranelift-frontend  cranelift-module  cranelift-object
    rspirv  rspirv-reflect  spirv-tools
    mlir-sys  melior                      (for §§ 15_MLIR dialect)
    z3-sys   cvc5-sys                     (for §§ 20_SMT)
    logos    chumsky                      (lexer + parser)
    level-zero-sys                        (L0 bindings for R18)
    ash                                   (Vulkan bindings)
    windows-rs                            (for D3D12 + sysman-Windows)
    metal (Apple-crate)                   (for Metal, when built-on-Mac)
  output : x86-64 obj (ELF + COFF) + SPIR-V blobs + fat-binary linker
  feature-set : F1..F6 minimum-viable (full design, minimal polish)

§ STAGE-1 SELF-HOST
  stage0 compiles stage1 source → stage1 binary
  stage1 compiles itself → stage1-prime (fixed-point check)
  own-x86-64-backend replaces Cranelift (§§ 14_BACKEND)
  all features F1..F6 + R1..R18 present

§ STAGE-2 LoA MIGRATION
  Odin-LoA-v10 (`C:\Users\Apocky\source\repos\LoA v10`) → CSSLv3-LoA-v11
  engine-primitives native (no wrappers) • F6 observability everywhere
  orthogonal-persistence R13 enables session-continuity across rebuild

§ STAGE-3 C99 REPRODUCIBILITY (R16)
  ∀ compiler-version emits self-compiling C99-tarball
  any-C99-compiler rebuilds stage1 from-source
  ≡ PRIME-DIRECTIVE audit : third-party can-verify consent-encoded
  ≡ no zig1.wasm-style binary-blob cope

§ EXECUTION (no time-cap)
  Phase-A    : spec-corpus complete         (this chat)
  Phase-B    : Claude-Code handoff          (next chat)
  Phase-C    : implementation bursts        (solo Apocky + Claude-pair)
  self-host  : ≤ 2 weeks elapsed  ( ¬ 24 months)
  vertical-slice (§§ 21) : ≤ 4 weeks elapsed

